20to%20follow%20for%20questioning%20a%20common%20man%20and%20a%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20this%20Court%20holds%20that%20this%20Court%20would%20not%20lay%20down%20two%20different%20categories%20of%20laws%2C%20one%20for%20common%20citizens%2C%20and%20the%20other%20granting%20special%20privilege%20to%20be%20extended%20by%20investigating%20agency%20to%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20or%20any%20other%20person%20in%20power%20only%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20being%20in%20that%20public%20office%20since%20that%20public%20office%20is%20enjoyed%20by%20that%20public%20figure%20due%20to%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20said%20in%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20high%20court%20judgment%2C%20AAP%20leader%20and%20Delhi%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20said%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI%20did%20not%20find%20even%20a%20rupee%20during%20their%20searches%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20talking%20about%20crores.%20But%20ED%20and%20CBI%20have%20not%20found%20even%20a%20rupee%20of%20illegal%20money.%20Witnesses%20have%20been%20pressured%20to%20change%20their%20statements%20and%20say%20what%20ED%20wants%20them%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20issue%20is%20not%20about%20money%20laundering.%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20political%20conspiracy%20in%20India's%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bharadwaj%20also%20said%20that%20the%20high%20court%20had%20denied%20relief%20to%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20on%20the%20same%20grounds%2C%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20him%20bail.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20too%2C%20will%20get%20justice%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20a%20day%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%20but%20later%20withdrew%20his%20petition%20to%20raise%20the%20matter%20in%20the%20trial%20court.%20This%20was%20on%20the%20same%20day%20on%20which%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20refused%20relief%20to%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20leader%20K%20Kavitha%2C%20also%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20The%20top%20court%20had%20then%20said%20it%20cannot%20bypass%20protocol%20and%20asked%20Ms%20Kavitha%20to%20approach%20the%20trial%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighteen%20days%20and%20a%20court%20setback%20later%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20back%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20alleged%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20liquor%20policy%2C%20introduced%20in%202021%20and%20withdrawn%20the%20next%20year%2C%20provided%20under%20benefits%20to%20liquor%20licencees.%20Following%20a%20recommendation%20from%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%2C%20the%20CBI%20started%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20irregularities.%20The%20ED%20is%20probing%20the%20money%20trail%20in%20the%20case.%20Besides%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20Manish%20Sisodia%20is%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20case.%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20same%20case%2C%20is%20out%20on%20bail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712722080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4t8b8ev8_arvind-kejriwal-ani-650_650x400_04_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-moves-supreme-court-against-his-arrest-in-liquor-policy-case-after-high-court-setback-5410271%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20his%20petition%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http