%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20also%20been%20some%20speculation%20over%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E's%20inclusion%20in%20the%20side%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20with%20some%20experts%20and%20fans%20questioning%20his%20strike%20rate%20despite%20Kohli%20scoring%20a%20lot%20of%20runs%20in%20IPL%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20report%20claims%20that%20there%20are%20no%20question%20marks%20over%20Kohli's%20place%20in%20the%20side%20and%20with%20more%20than%20300%20runs%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20already%2C%20he%20has%20already%20made%20a%20strong%20case%20for%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Brian%20Lara%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F269-brian-lara-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBrian%20Lara%3C%2Fa%3E%20asserted%20that%20Virat%20Kohli's%20value%20transcends%20cold%20numbers%2C%20and%20the%20West%20Indian%20virtuoso%20has%20little%20doubt%20that%20the%20star%20batter%20should%20be%20a%20part%20of%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20stood%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20a%20social%20media%20storm%20after%20making%20a%2067-ball%20hundred%20for%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20against%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20in%20their%20IPL%202024%20match%20at%20Jaipur%2C%20which%20was%20the%20joint%20slowest%20hundred%20in%20the%20competition%20alongside%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Manish%20Pandey%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1045-manish-pandey-playerprofile%5C%22%3EManish%20Pandey%3C%2Fa%3E's%20century%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20strike-rate%20depends%20on%20position%2C%20and%20for%20an%20opener%20strike-rate%20of%20130-140%20is%20pretty%20alright.%20But%20if%20you%20are%20coming%20in%20the%20middle-order%20then%20you%20may%20be%20required%20to%20hit%20at%20150%20or%20