20Swiggy%20and%20fantasy%20sports%20platform%20Dream11%20worth%20USD%208%20billion%20each%2C%20and%20Razorpay%20worth%20USD%207.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20factor%20is%20that%20Indian%20founders%20produced%20more%20offshore%20unicorns%20than%20any%20other%20country%2C%20co-founding%20109%20unicorns%20outside%20of%20India%20compared%20with%20just%2067%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20unicorns%20founded%20outside%20of%20India%2C%20significantly%20all%20were%20in%20the%20US%20(95)%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20with%20four%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20three%20in%20Singapore%2C%20and%20two%20in%20Germany%2C%20the%20Index%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20active%20city%20for%20unicorns%20outside%20of%20the%20US%20and%20China%20was%20London%2C%20followed%20by%20Bengaluru%2C%20Paris%20and%20Berlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20world's%20most%20successful%20unicorn%20investors%2C%20led%20by%20Tiger%20Global%2C%20Softbank%20and%20HongShan%2C%20highlighted%20the%20symbiotic%20relationship%20between%20startups%20and%20strategic%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20investments%20in%20startups%2C%20it%20said%20the%20year%202024%20has%20seen%20a%20slowdown%20in%20new%20unicorn%20investments%2C%20especially%20compared%20with%20the%20heyday%20of%202021%20as%20investor%20exits%20prove%20harder%20to%20come%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20record-breaking%20stock%20markets%20in%20the%20US%2C%20India%20and%20the%20UK%20have%20not%20delivered%20significant%20unicorn%20IPOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20this%20list%20of%20the%20world's%20unicorns%20can%20inspire%20individuals%20to%20drive%20value%20creation%20in%20new%20sectors%20and%20for%20countries%20and%20cities%20to%20recognise%20the%20importance%20of%20unicorns%20to%20their%20future%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20some%20will%20fail%2C%20and%20when%20they%20do%20it%20is%20normally%20to%20massive%20media%20attention%2C%20such%20as%20India%20education%20platform%20BYJU%2C%20but%20on%20the%20whole%20unicorns%20are%20seen%20as%20inherently%20vital%20to%20the%20new%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20unicorns%20come%20from%2053%20countries%2C%20up%20from%2048%20last%20year%2C%20spread%20around%20291%20cities%2C%20up%20from%20271.%20The%20US%20led%20with%20703%20unicorns%2C%20followed%20by%20China%20with%20340.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHurun%20found%201%2C453%20unicorns%20across%20the%20world%2C%20a%20new%20world%20record%20and%20up%207%20per%20cent%20or%2092%20unicorns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712719860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-07%2Fellgarqg_laptop-generic-650_625x300_09_July_21.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findians-founded-highest-unicorns-outside-country-report-5410232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indians%20have%20founded%20more%20offshore%20unicorns%20than%20any%20other%20country%2C%20co-founding%20109%20unicorns%20outside%20of%20India%20compared%20with%2067%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Global%20Unicorn%20Index%202024%2C%20a%20ranking%20of%20the%20world's%20start-ups%20founded%20in%20the%202000s.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findians-founded-highest-unicorns-outside-country-report-5410232%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findians-founded-highest-unicorns-outside-country-report-5410232%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findians-founded-highest-unicorns-outside-country-report-5410232%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%