di%20is%20the%20best%20person%20to%20lead%20India%20at%20this%20critical%20juncture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20reason%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20he%20had%20unconditionally%20decided%20to%20support%20the%20alliance%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20-%20who%20had%20staged%20a%20rebellion%20against%20the%20MNS%20chief's%20estranged%20cousin%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20in%202022%20-%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20any%20expectations.%20When%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20strong%20leadership%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20will%20back%20the%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP%20unconditionally.%20It%20is%20only%20for%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20whether%20the%20MNS%20will%20field%20any%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20asked%20his%20cadre%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20later%20this%20year%2C%20indicating%20that%20he%20is%20hoping%20for%20support%20and%20a%20share%20of%20seats%20when%20they%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'What%20Was%20Wrong%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20his%20meeting%20with%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%2055-year-old%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20wrong%20in%20me%20going%20and%20meeting%20the%20home%20minister%3F%20The%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20told%20me%20we%20should%20come%20together.%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20also%20spoke%20(about%20this).%20That's%20why%20I%20met%20Amit%20Shah.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20he%20was%20the%20first%20person%20in%20the%20country%20to%20say%20Narendra%20Modi%20should%20be%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said%20he%20had%20also%20opposed%20him%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%202014%2C%