%3Cp%3ETo%20qualify%20for%20a%20lottery%20apartment%2C%20each%20household%20must%20meet%20specific%20income%20and%20size%20requirements%2C%20and%20these%20vary%20across%20the%20developments%20depending%20on%20unit%20size%20and%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202013%2C%20there%20have%20been%20more%20than%2025%20million%20applications%20submitted%20for%20about%2040%2C000%20units%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2Fnyregion%2Fnyc-affordable-housing-lottery.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F01%2F11%2Frealestate%2Fbetter-than-the-powerball.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eodds%20of%20winning%20the%20housing%20lottery%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%201%20in%20592%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%20The%20HPD%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplying%20for%20the%20housing%20lottery%20was%20a%20long%20process%20that%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20patience%20and%20paperwork%2C%20and%20Brown%20ran%20into%20a%20few%20hiccups%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%20me%20maybe%20over%20a%20year%20before%20I%20started%20hearing%20back%20from%20different%20properties%20that%20I%20applied%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20them%20I%20ended%20up%20not%20qualifying%20for%2C%20some%20of%20them%20I%20didn't%20provide%20enough%20documentation%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nyc.gov%2Fassets%2Fhpd%2Fdownloads%2Fpdfs%2Fservices%2Fafter-you-apply-english.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaperwork%3C%2Fa%3E%20included%20pay%20stubs%2C%20tax%20returns%2C%20as%20well%20as%20receipts%20for%20rent%20and%20recent%20gas%20or%20electric%20bills%20from%20where%20she%20had%20been%20living%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660a6a3316bde8d4ead3f565%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224169%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20room%20is%20bright%20and%20airy.%3Cp%3ENkenge%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20getting%20the%20news%20that%20she%20qualified%20for%20an%20apartment%2C%20it%20took%20another%20three%20months%20before%20she%20was%20able%20to%20move%20in%20at%20the%20start%20of%20May%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20submitting%20documents%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20February%20and%20getting%20things%20rolling%20in%20terms%20of%20being%20accepted%20by%20the%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown's%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20is%20located%20in%20Chelsea%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20on%20the%20west%20side%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-studio-apartment-listing-no-bathroom-instagram-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManhattan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-renter-landlord-overcharged-rent-stabilized-apartment-lawsuit-backpay-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erent%20is%20stabilized%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20a%20two-year%20lease%20with%20an%20option%20for%20renewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20apartment%20costs%20%241%2C081%20a%20month%2C%20but%20since%20she%20gets%20a%20utility%20allowance%20of%20%2485%2C%20she%20ends%20up%20paying%20%24996%20for%20rent%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20additional%20%2454%20monthly%20for%20amenity%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20median%20monthly%20rent%20for%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Chelsea%20is%20%245%2C232%2C%20per%20the%20latest%20April%20data%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.renthop.com%2Faverage-rent-in%2Fchelsea-new-york-ny%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERentCafe.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20day%20I%20moved%20in%2C%20I%20was%20super%20excited.%20I%20felt%20blessed%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%20things%20were%20coming%20together%2C%20with%20the%20opportunity%20for%20me%20to%20take%20my%20business%20to%20the%20next%20level%20in%20a%20way%20where%20I%20don't%20feel%20stressed%20out%20about%20bills%20and%20all%20the%20things%20that%20adulting%20has%20to%20offer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20apartment%20came%20with%20some%20standard%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshoppers-buying-smart-fridge-craft-ice-washer-dryer-machine-lowes-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappliances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20washer%20and%20dryer%2C%20a%20dishwasher%2C%20and%20a%20refrigerator%2C%20although%20she%20says%20that's%20not%20always%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plants%20in%20front%20of%20a%20big%20standing%20mirror.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660a6a3316bde8d4ead3f566%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224396%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrown%20is%20a%20proud%20plant%20mom.%3Cp%3ENkenge%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20apartments%20that%20offer%20different%20things%2C%20so%20it's%20just%20up%20to%20you%20as%20the%20applicant%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20ones%20that%20you%20want%20or%20that%20you're%20open%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20housing%20lottery%20website%20has%20a%20list%20of%20amenities%20displayed%20for%20each%20apartment%20block%2C%20it%20doesn't%20specify%20which%20appliances%20each%20apartment%20within%20the%20block%20has%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20in%20this%20building%20that%20I'm%20in%2C%20there%20are%20quite%20a%20few%20apartments%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20one%20of%20them%20may%20not%20have%20a%20washer%20and%20dryer%2C%20whereas%20another%20one.%20But%20they%20don't%20tell%20you%20in%20detail%20which%20of%20these%20apartments%20they%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20potential%20tenants%20have%20to%20submit%20all%20their%20documents%20even%20before%20they%20can%20view%20the%20apartment%20in%20person%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20workspace%20corner.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660a6a3316bde8d4ead3f564%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20corner%20of%20her%20bedroom%20is%20turned%20into%20a%20workspace.%3Cp%3ENkenge%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20that%20you%20may%20not%20even%20want%20the%20place%2C%20but%20you%20still%20have%20to%20submit%20your%20documents%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20space%20of%20one's%20own%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrown's%20home%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20her%20personality%20and%20all%20the%20things%20she%20loves%3A%20bright%20colors%2C%20eclectic%20furniture%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-really-love-plants-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%2040%20houseplants%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlants%20have%20a%20way%20of%20really%20transforming%20your%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%20not%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20health%20benefits%2C%20with%20oxygen%20and%20everything%2C%20but%20also%20in%20nurturing%20your%20plant%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20brought%20most%20of%20her%20furniture%20and%20decor%20over%20from%20her%20old%20apartment%20and%20succeeded%20in%20turning%20her%20new%20space%20into%20the%20cozy%2C%20airy%20home%20she%20had%20always%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pinterest.com%2Fitsnkenge%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvisioned%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20counter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660a6a3316bde8d4ead3f567%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224371%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20counter.%3Cp%3ENkenge%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAesthetics%20aside%2C%20most%20of%20her%20furniture%20pieces%20double%20as%20storage%20space%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20things%2C%20so%20I%20always%20try%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20hide%20them%20away%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20make%20the%20space%20look%20comfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20I%20have%20a%20couple%20of%20Ottomans%20that%20have%20storage%20%E2%80%94%20you%20just%20open%20up%20the%20top.%20The%20ottomans%20themselves%20look%20very%20cute%2C%20and%20you%20can%20sit%20on%20them.%20They%20don't%20take%20up%20too%20much%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20pick%20a%20favorite%20spot%20in%20the%20home%2C%20but%20if%20she%20had%20to%20choose%2C%20it'll%20be%20the%20corner%20by%20her%20southeast-facing%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pink%20and%20yellow%20curtains%2C%20together%20with%20her%20plants%20and%20a%20little%20seated%20area%20by%20the%20window%2C%20remind%20her%20of%20a%20caf%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224194%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20nook%20by%20a%20window.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660a6a333f923f7dab02f834%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224799%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20nook%20by%20the%20window.%3Cp%3ENkenge%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20really%20inspired%20by%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20especially%20the%20ones%20in%20Paris.%20And%20I%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20would%20have%20the%20chairs%20facing%20outward%2C%20and%20I%20really%20liked%20that.%20So%20if%20anything%2C%20I%20was%20just%20bringing%20that%20into%20my%20home%20as%20well%2C%26quot