red%20males%20were%20located.%20EMS%20responded%20and%20determined%20two%20males%2C%20a%2049-year-old%20and%20a%2057-year-old%20were%20deceased%2C%20and%20a%2051-year-old%20male%20was%20seriously%20injured.%20Paramedics%20transported%20the%20surviving%20male%20to%20hospital%20with%20serious%20life-threatening%20injuries%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20press%20release%2C%20the%20Edmonton%20Police%20Service%20said%20that%20the%20homicide%20section%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20investigation%20and%20police%20are%20not%20looking%20for%20any%20suspects.%20The%20police%20stated%20that%20the%20autopsies%20have%20been%20scheduled%20for%20Tuesday%20and%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20one%20of%20the%20victims%20has%20identified%20him%20as%20Buta%20Singh%20Gill%2C%20owner%20of%20Edmonton-based%20Gill%20Built%20Homes%2C%20CTV%20News%20Edmonton%20reported.%20At%20least%2050%20people%20gathered%20at%20the%20site%20on%20Monday%20afternoon%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20were%20members%20of%20the%20South%20Asian%20home-building%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Edmonton%20Police%20Service%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BPolice%20are%20asking%20citizens%20to%20avoid%20the%20area%20of%20Cavanagh%20Blvd%20SW%20and%2030%20Avenue%20SW%20while%20police%20investigate%20a%20shooting%20that%20occurred%20in%20the%20residential%20area%20around%20noon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20immediate%20concerns%20for%20public%20safety%20at%20this%20time%20and%20responding%20officers%20have%20secured%20the%20scene.%20EPS%20homicide%20investigators%20will%20be%20leading%20this%20investigation.%20No%20further%20details%20are%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Edmonton%20city%20councillor%20and%20former%20EPS%20member%20Mohinder%20Banga%20said%20he%20came%20to%20the%20site%20of%20the%20incident%20after%20hearing%20Gill%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20shooting%2C%20CTV%20News%20Edmonton%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohinder%20Banga%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20such%20a%20nice%20person%2C%20and%20he%20would%20jump%20in%20to%20help%20people%20whenever%20they%20needed%20help%20and%20without%20looking%20for%20anything%20in%20return.%20That%20was%20his%20quality.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20you%20can%20see%20all%20the%20people%20here%2C%20they're%20all%20well-wishers%20and%20the%20community%20is%20in%20shock%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELindsay%20Hilton%2C%20a%20woman%20who%20said%20she%20witnessed%20the%20shooting%20while%20heading%20home%2C%20said%20she%20saw%20a%20man%20walking%20down%20Cavanagh%20Boulevard%20wearing%20construction%20attire.%20She%20said%20a%20black%20car%20came%20out%20of%20a%20nearby%20construction%20site%2C%20did%20a%20U-turn%2C%20drove%20up%20behind%20the%20man%20and%20bumped%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20CTV%20News%20Edmonton%2C%20Hilton%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20man%20in%20the%20construction%20vest%20had%20his%20gun%20out%2C%20pointed%20at%20the%20car%20and%20shot%20once%20into%20the%20driver's%20side%20window%2C%20then%20I%20went%20right%20around%20the%20corner%20because%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20was%20going%20to%20happen.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20heard%20two%20more%20gunshots%20following.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHilton%20said%20she%20pulled%20over%20and%20called%20911.%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20had%20moments%20of%20breaking%20down%20like%20this%20into%20tears%20because%20it's%20just%20something%20I%20think%20that%20you%20just%20don't%20expect%20to%20see%20in%20broad%20daylight%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20CTV%20News%20Edmonton%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20looked%20like%20another%20interaction%20of%20guys%20stopping%20to%20talk%20at%20the%20construction%20site%2C%20so%20when%20I%20saw%20him%20pull%20that%20gun%20and%20shoot%2C%20it%20just%20t