.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-finance-editorial-standards%23rating-banking-product%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20banking%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222848%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jennifer%20Sisson%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b923d7ac2de4f17ee5d451%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221424%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Jennifer%20Sisson.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Sisson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI've%20always%20dreamed%20of%20visiting%20Italy%2C%20and%20after%20years%20of%20saving%20I%20finally%20had%20enough.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit%20I%20put%20off%20my%20trip%2C%20and%20my%20travel%20fund%20sat%20in%20a%20high-yield%20savings%20account.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20interest%20rates%20low%2C%20I%20thought%20I'd%20earn%20more%20by%20investing%20in%20the%20market.%20I%20was%20wrong.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-high-interest-accounts-today%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20my%20life%2C%20I%20have%20dreamed%20of%20going%20to%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20my%20dad%20would%20show%20me%20slideshows%20(the%20old%20carousel%20kind)%20from%20his%20two-year%20church%20mission%20and%20business%20trips%20there.%20I%20was%20enchanted%20by%20the%20sculptures%2C%20frescoes%2C%20and%20breathtaking%20architecture.%20I%20read%20%26quot%3BThe%20Agony%20and%20the%20Ecstasy%26quot%3B%20and%20studied%20the%20Renaissance%20in%20European%20history%20my%20junior%20year%20of%20high%20school%2C%20and%20I%20was%20completely%20hooked%20%E2%80%94%20Italy%20was%20at%20the%20top%20of%20my%20bucket%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20actually%20start%20saving%20for%20the%20trip%20until%20I%20was%2035.%20My%20family%20was%20in%20dire%20financial%20straits%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20I%20looked%20around%20me%20one%20day%20and%20realized%20that%20if%20I%20didn't%20start%20saving%20money%20for%20this%20long-held%20goal%2C%20I'd%20die%20someday%20having%20dreamed%20of%20Italy%20but%20never%20gone.%20That%20thought%20was%20terrifying.%20So%20I%20found%20an%20old%20coffee%20can%2C%20plunked%20some%20loose%20change%20into%20it%2C%20and%20labeled%20it%20%26quot%3BItaly%20fund.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20that%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20Texas%20to%20a%20new%20job%20with%20a%20lot%20more%20stability.%20Things%20started%20looking%20up%20financially%2C%20and%20a%20few%20years%20after%20the%20first%20coins%20went%20into%20the%20coffee%20can%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20squirrel%20away%20around%20%241%2C200%20and%20nearly%20enough%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-travel-rewards-credit-cards%5C%22%3Eairline%20and%20hotel%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20my%20husband%20and%20me%20to%20Italy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20this%20time%2C%20my%20Italy%20fund%20had%20graduated%20from%20the%20coffee%20can%20to%20an%20online%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Ehigh-yield%20savings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20earning%20the%20highest%20interest%20rate%20of%20any%20savings%20account%20I%20could%20find%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20a%20whopping%201.05%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20itinerary%20was%20planned%2C%20dates%20picked%2C%20childcare%20arranged.%20Then%20the%20pandemic%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20moved%20my%20travel%20money%20to%20the%20stock%20market%20hoping%20to%20earn%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20news%20came%20out%20about%20how%20bad%20COVID-19%20numbers%20were%20in%20Italy%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20tabled%20the%20trip%2C%20hoping%20to%20make%20it%20in%202021.%20As%20time%20wore%20on%2C%20lockdowns%20and%20restrictions%20stayed%20firmly%20in%20place%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20be%20quite%20some%20time%20before%20I%20would%20be%20comfortable%20traveling%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20continued%20to%20sit%20in%20my%20pent-up%20wanderlust%2C%20I%20watched%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-the-stock-market%5C%22%3Estock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20climb%20to%20unprecedented%20levels.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-ira-accounts%5C%22%3EIRA%3C%2Fa%3E%20grew%20by%20leaps%20and%20bounds%20while%20my%20Italy%20fund%20sat%20sad%20and%20unused%20in%20my%20savings%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20financial%20FOMO%20began%20to%20set%20in.%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20stupid.%20Why%20not%20put%20my%20Italy%20fund%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-online-brokerage%5C%22%3Ebrokerage%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20get%20the%20double-digit%20returns%20I%20can%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20instead%20of%201%25%20in%20a%20'high-yield'%20savings%20account%3F%20If%20I%20do%20that%2C%20I'll%20have%20way%20more%20money%20to%20spend%20on%20gelato%20once%20the%20pandemic%20lifts.%26quot%3B%20It%20made%20perfect%20sense%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20I%20soon%20came%20to%20realize%20how%20short-sighted%20that%20decision%20was.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20transferred%20the%20contents%20of%20my%20high-yield%20savings%20account%20to%20a%20brokerage%20account%20and%20bought%20several%20of%20the%20stocks%20and%20ETFs%20that%20had%20been%20riding%20high%20during%20the%20pandemic%3A%20Tesla%2C%20Pinterest%2C%20and%20tech-focused%20ARK%20funds.%20(I'm%20cringing%20as%20I%20write%20this.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20lost%20money%20when%20the%20stock%20market%20started%20tanking%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20COVID-19%20restrictions%20began%20to%20ease%2C%20I%20began%20researching%20flights%20and%20hotels%20to%20make%20travel%20plans%20again.%20But%20I%20looked%20in%20my%20brokerage%20account%2C%20and%20now%20I%20had%20less%20than%20half%20the%20money%20I'd%20started%20with.%20Tech%20stocks%20took%20a%20beating%20after%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20I'd%20put%20most%20of%20my%20savings.%20Between%20February%202021%20and%20October%202022%2C%20I'd%20lost%20%24665.%20That's%20a%20lot%20of%20gelato.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20chart%20shows%20losses%20in%20an%20investment%20account%20over%20time%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6345b88c39a9f1001232a639%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22605%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Sisson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20made%20the%20rookie%20mistake%20of%20putting%20short-term%20savings%20into%20long-term%20savings%20vehicles.%20I%20was%20raised%20by%20options-trading%20parents%20and%20I'm%20a%20personal%20finance%20writer%20by%20trade%2C%20so%20I%20have%20no%20good%20excuses%20for%20this.%20I%20knew%20better%20than%20to%20put%20my%20vacation%20money%20%E2%80%94%20money%20I%20knew%20I'd%20be%20spending%20in%20the%20next%20two%20or%20three%20years%2C%20max%20%E2%80%94%20into%20growth%20stocks%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20held%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years.%20I%20made%20a%20rash%20decision%20based%20on%20the%20two%20emotions%20you%20should%20never%20listen%20to%20when%20investing%3A%20greed%20and%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20now%20faced%20with%20the%20uncomfortable%20choice%20of%20selling%20my%20securities%20(ones%20I%20truly%20believe%20will%20do%20well%20in%20the%20coming%20years)%20and%20cutting%20my%20losses%2C%20or%20risk%20watching%20my%20Italy%20fund%20dwindle%20further.%20I'm%20still%20not%20sure%20which%20poison%20I'm%20going%20to%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20rising%20interest%20rates%2C%20so-called%20high-yield%20savings%20accounts%20look%20only%20mildly%20more%20attractive%20than