0like%20gazpacho%20and%20tortilla%20de%20patata%2C%20are%20made%20of%20inexpensive%20ingredients%20that%20are%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20spoiling%20(e.g.%2C%20tomatoes%20for%20gazpacho%20are%20best%20once%20they%20are%20overripe%2C%20soft%2C%20and%20have%20nearly%20gone%20bad).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGazpacho%20isn't%20for%20everyone%2C%20but%20anyone%20can%20benefit%20from%20buying%20local%2C%20in-season%20foods%20and%20meal%20planning%20around%20recipes%20that%20make%20grocery%20hauls%20last%20as%20long%20as%20possible.%20I%20save%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20a%20month%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fthe-best-credit-cards-for-buying-groceries%5C%22%3Egroceries%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20I%20discovered%20cheap%20alternatives%20to%20AC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lived%20in%20Texas%20most%20of%20my%20life%2C%20so%20I%20kept%20my%20AC%20cranked%20to%20max%20power%20almost%2024%2F7%20in%20the%20summer.%20When%20I%20moved%20to%20Spain%2C%20I%20had%20a%20tiny%20AC%20unit%20in%20my%20apartment%20that%20stopped%20working%20a%20month%20after%20my%20first%20night%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECentral%20AC%20is%20a%20rare%20luxury%20in%20southern%20Spain%2C%20and%20it%20was%20August%2C%20so%20I%20improvised%20by%20leaving%20the%20windows%20of%20my%20third-floor%20apartment%20open%20during%20the%20day%20to%20let%20the%20breeze%20in%20and%20keeping%20chilled%20towels%20and%20water%20in%20the%20fridge%20for%20especially%20hot%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20very%20little%20on%20my%20energy%20bill%20there%2C%20and%20now%20I%20am%20much%20more%20conscious%20of%20my%20energy%20use%20in%20the%20US%20despite%20living%20in%20Florida.%20These%20days%2C%20the%20AC%20is%20only%20on%20in%20the%20afternoons%20when%20I'm%20home%2C%20which%20saves%20me%20around%20%2437%20a%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20I%20switched%20to%20walking%2C%20biking%2C%20and%20carpooling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20I%20was%20used%20to%20having%20my%20own%20car%20and%20the%20freedom%20to%20go%20anywhere%2C%20anytime%2C%20without%20pause.%20This%20led%20to%20me%20burning%20a%20ton%20of%20unnecessary%20cash%20on%20gas.%20In%20Rota%2C%20I%20used%20a%20variety%20of%20methods%20to%20get%20around%2C%20since%20there%20is%20very%20little%20in%20the%20way%20of%20public%20transportation%20there.%20I%20biked%2C%20carpooled%2C%20and%20walked%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20met%20my%20husband%2C%20we%20drove%20his%202000%20Honda%20CRV%20%26quot%3Bbeater%26quot%3B%20infrequently%20because%20we%20were%20accustomed%20to%20walking%20and%20biking%20everywhere.%20Now%20that%20we're%20back%20in%20the%20States%2C%20we%20are%20much%20more%20conservative%20with%20gas%20usage%20and%20carpool%20to%20work%20as%20often%20as%20possible%2C%20which%20saves%20anywhere%20from%20%24116%20to%20%24230%20a%20week.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20I%20learned%20to%20drive%20standard%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband's%20Honda%20had%20a%20standard%20transmission.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20drive%20standard%2C%20but%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20pay%20less%20for%20rental%20cars%20when%20we%20went%20on%20trips%2C%20since%20automatic%20cars%20are%20not%20the%20norm%20in%20Europe.%20Once%20I%20learned%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20rent%20cars%20for%20much%20less%20and%20saved%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20on%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20love%20driving%20stick%2C%20and%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20saved%20more%20than%20%241%2C000%20by%20buying%20the%20standard%20version%20of%20my%20car.%20In%20the%20long%20run%2C%20it%20paid%20to%20take%20the%20time%20to%20learn%20that%20relatively%20simple%20skill%2C%20and%20it%20has%20driven%20me%20(pun%20intended)%20to%20be%20more%20resourceful%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20managing%20my%20finances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20I%20stopped%20spending%20on%20things%20and%20chose%20experiences%20instead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20tiny%20Spanish%20apartment%2C%20I%20had%20very%20little%20room%20for%20things.%20I%20had%20very%20few%20clothes%2C%20a%20few%20books%2C%20my%20uniforms%2C%20and%20my%20bike.%20I%20was%20constantly%20at%20work%20on%20the%20ship%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20have%20time%20to%20accumulate%20stuff%2C%20even%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20cram%20it%20into%20that%20small%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20realized%20that%20the%20experience%20of%20being%20on%20assignment%20overseas%20cultivated%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bunsettled%26quot%3B%20or%20unattached%20to%20one%20place.%20I%20didn't%20buy%20things%20I%20wanted%20simply%20because%20I%20knew%20I%20would%20have%20to%20move%20them%20back%20to%20the%20US%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20time.%20Instead%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-travel-rewards-credit-cards%5C%22%3Espend%20my%20money%20on%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20(in%20my%20experience)%20more%20fulfilling%20than%20harboring%20a%20collection%20of%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20only%20lived%20abroad%20for%20a%20short%20time%2C%20the%20experience%20changed%20my%20approach%20to%20money%20and%20still%20influences%20my%20spending%20and%20saving%20habits.%20I%20learned%20that%20saving%20a%20ton%20of%20money%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20complicated%3A%20Sometimes%2C%20it's%20as%20easy%20as%20incorporating%20a%20bit%20of%20frugality%20and%20resourcefulness%20into%20the%20budget%20plan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20Exclusive%20Savings%20with%20Raisin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Open%20one%20of%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3E%20best%20savings%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20no-fee%20Raisin%20account%20in%20minutes%20and%20spread%20your%20savings%20across%20an%20exclusive%20network%20of%20over%2030%20FDIC-insured%20banks%20and%20NCUA-insured%20credit%20unions.%20Earn%20top%20savings%20rates%20and%20manage%20it%20all%20with%20a%20single%20secure%20login.%20Read%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fraisin-review%5C%22%3ERaisin%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20July%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-abroad-money-lessons-saving-thousands-navy-2024-04%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712699281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62deba07bd18c30019d1ae60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-abroad-money-lessons-saving-thousands-navy-2024-04%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Victoria%20Cavazos%20lived%20in%20Rota%2C%20Spain%2C%20while%20on%20assignment%20with%20the%20Navy.%20She%20learned%20to%20spend%20on%20experiences%20instead%20of%20things.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Victoria%20Cavazos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-abroad-money-lessons-saving-thousands-navy-2024-04%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boeing%20hit%20after%20new%20whistleblower%20raises%20concerns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712699255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10C7B%2Fproduction%2F_133113786_whatsubject.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68775413%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boeing%20shares%20dropped%20almost%202%25%20after%20concerns%20were%20raised%20over%20its%20787%20and%20777%20jets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3