hed%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712687760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fmh11kjs8_byju-raveendran-afp-650_625x300_01_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funicorns-decline-in-india-byjus-valuation-loss-steepest-globally-hurun-global-unicorn-index-2024-5408085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20number%20of%20unicorns%20--%20companies%20worth%20over%20USD%201%20billion%20--%20in%20the%20country%20has%20declined%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20four%20years%20to%2067%2C%20a%20report%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funicorns-decline-in-india-byjus-valuation-loss-steepest-globally-hurun-global-unicorn-index-2024-5408085%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funicorns-decline-in-india-byjus-valuation-loss-steepest-globally-hurun-global-unicorn-index-2024-5408085%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funicorns-decline-in-india-byjus-valuation-loss-steepest-globally-hurun-global-unicorn-index-2024-5408085%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Child%20Sex%20Abuse%20Cases%20Can't%20Be%20Dismissed%20Based%20On%20%26quot%3BCompromise%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20observed%20that%20crimes%20under%20'Special%20Statutes'%20like%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20or%20POCSO%20can't%20be%20dismissed%20merely%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bcompromise%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20victim%20and%20the%20offender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20minor%20prosecutrix%20is%20immaterial%20for%20registration%20of%20the%20offence%2C%20then%20such%20consent%20shall%20still%20remain%20immaterial%20for%20all%20practical%20purposes%20at%20all%20the%20stages%20including%20for%20compromise.%20Merely%20because%20the%20minor%20prosecutrix%20has%20later%20on%20agreed%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20compromise%20with%20the%20applicant%2C%20would%20not%20be%20sufficient%20to%20quash%20the%20proceedings%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20single%20judge%20bench%20of%20justice%20Samit%20Gopal%20in%20a%20decision%20on%20April%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20presided%20over%20a%20petition%20seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20criminal%20proceedings%20against%20the%20accused%20who%20claimed%20that%20after%20the%20filing%20of%20the%20case%2C%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20investigation%20and%20summoning%20of%20the%20applicant%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20for%20the%20alleged%20offences%2C%20a%20compromise%20was%20reached%20between%20the%20parties%2C%20so%20the%20pending%20case%20be%20decided%20accordingly.%20The%20counsel%20for%20the%20victim%20also%20supported%20the%20petition%20of%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20of%20the%20state%20opposing%20the%20accused-applicant's%20petition%2C%20said%20the%20victim%2C%20who%20was%2015%20when%20the%20crime%20first%20happened%2C%20was%20subjected%20to%20sexual%20assault%20over%20a%20period%20of%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clear%20that%20where%20the%20prosecutrix%20is%20a%20minor%20below%2018%20years%20of%20age%2C%20then%20her%20consent%20would%20be%20immaterial.%20When%20an%20offence%20is%20made%20out%20against%20the%20accused%20irrespective%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20whether%20the%20prosecutrix%20was%20a%20consenting%20party%20or%20not%2C%20then%20certainly%2C%20the%20prosecution%20cannot%20be%20quashed%20merely%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20at%20a%20later%20stage%20the%20prosecutrix%20has%20entered%20into%20a%20compromise%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20making%20the%20observations%2C%20the%20judge%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%202014%20judgments%20where%20it%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSuch%20a%20power%20is%20not%20be%20exercised%20in%20those%20prosecutions%20which%20involve%20heinous%20and%20serious%20offences%20of%20mental%20depravity%20or%20offences%20like%20murder%2C%20rape%2C%20dacoity%2C%20etc.%20Such%20offences%20are%20not%20private%20in%20nature%20and%20have%20a%20serious%20impact%20on%20society%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712686920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-10%2Fb45r6snk_allahabad-high-court_650x400_26_October_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchild-sex-abuse-cases-cant-be-dismissed-based-on-compromise-high-court-5408644%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20observed%20that%20crimes%20under%20'Special%20Statutes'%20like%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20or%20POCSO%20can't%20be%20dismissed%20merely%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bcompromise%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20victim%20and%20the%20offender.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchild-sex-abuse-cases-cant-be-dismissed-based-on-compromise-high-court-5408644%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchild-sex-abuse-cases-cant-be-dismissed-based-on-compromise-high-court-5408644%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchild-sex-abuse-cases-cant-be-dismissed-based-on-compromise-high-court-5408644%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Milestone%20march%3A%20Sensex%20makes%20pit%20stop%20at%2075%2C000%2C%20ends%20in%20the%20red%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712686846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F09%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1712686767-9118.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fstock-market-news%2Fbse-sensex-hits-all-time-high-crosses-75-000-nifty50