0Pawar%2C%20in%20the%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Pune%20district.%20Sule%20is%20the%20candidate%20of%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaramati%2C%20from%20where%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20an%20MLA%2C%20is%20the%20home%20turf%20of%20the%20Pawar%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...You%20have%20been%20with%20the%20Pawars%20for%20so%20long%2C%20but%20now%20there%20must%20be%20some%20thought%20about%20what%20to%20do%20(in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls)%20as%20there%20are%20two%20candidates%20from%20the%20same%20family.%20You%20must%20be%20wondering%20whom%20to%20support%2C%20whom%20to%20vote%20for.%20It%20is%20simple%2C%20as%20you%20have%20been%20with%20the%20Pawars%20for%20so%20long%2C%20just%20go%20and%20vote%20for%20(another)%20Pawar%20(referring%20to%20Sunetra%20Pawar)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20CM%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20ruling%20NCP%2C%20was%20speaking%20at%20a%20programme%20of%20party%20workers%20in%20Baramati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20voting%20for%20(Sunetra)%20Pawar%2C%20people%20won't%20be%20breaking%20the%20tradition%20of%20supporting%20the%20family%2C%20said%20the%20deputy%20CM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecall%20the%201991%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20when%20you%20elected%20the%20son%2C%20meaning%20me.%20Later%2C%20you%20elected%20the%20father%2C%20meaning%20Pawar%20Saheb%2C%20and%20after%20that%20you%20voted%20for%20the%20daughter%2C%20meaning%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20for%20three%20consecutive%20terms.%20Now%2C%20just%20go%20and%20elect%20the%20daughter-in-law%20(Sunetra%20Pawar).%20Everything%20will%20be%20balanced%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20leader%20added%20that%20by%20doing%20this%2C%20everyone%20--%20son%2C%20father%2C%20daughter%2C%20and%20daughter-in-law%20--%20will%20be%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20potshots%20at%20his%20cousins%20and%20family%20members%20who%20are%20currently%20opposing%20him%20and%20siding%20with%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20the%20deputy%20CM%20said%20in%20none%20of%20his%20elections%20his%20cousins%20campaigned%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20now%20all%20are%20working.%20You%20(cousins)%20did%20not%20feel%20like%20working%20for%20me%20when%20I%20contested%20elections.%20Are%20you%20going%20to%20work%20after%20this%20election%3F%20There%20will%20only%20be%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20his%20party%20workers%20and%20no%20one%20will%20be%20there.%20Their%20(family%20members)%20work%20is%20temporary.%20They%20are%20like%20mushrooms%20that%20grow%20in%20rains%20but%20after%20polls%2C%20all%20these%20mushrooms%20will%20go%20on%20foreign%20trips%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%20said%20he%20is%20exercising%20restraint%20while%20speaking%2C%20but%20if%20he%20decides%20to%20speak%20openly%2C%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20for%20many%20of%20these%20people%20to%20move%20in%20public%20or%20show%20their%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20not%20force%20me%20to%20open%20my%20mouth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned%20his%20family%20detractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20to%20the%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%20will%20be%20held%20in%20five%20phases%20from%20April%2019%20to%20May%2020.%20In%20Baramati%2C%20polling%20will%20be%20held%20on%20May%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712684940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fi8k655sg_ajit-pawar_625x300_25_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felect-sharad-pawars-daughter-in-law-from-baramati-ajit-pawar-5408383%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20on%20Tuesday%20sought%20support%20for%20his%20wife%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20sent%20out%20a%20message%20to%20Baramati%20voters%2C%20telling%20the