-sabha-election%2Fcong-ceding-the-pole-position-in-alliance-to-thackeray-led-shiv-sena-ubt-124040901015_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCredibility%20In%20Serious%20Danger%26quot%3B%3A%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20On%20Kamal%20Nath%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20record%20loss%20for%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Digvijaya%20Singh%2C%20a%20record%20victory%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Congress's%20last%20citadel%2C%20Chhindwara%20--%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20appeared%20more%20than%20confident%20about%20his%20party's%20performance%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20win%20all%2029%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20That%20includes%20Rajgarh%2C%20from%20where%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20is%20contesting%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Chhindwara%2C%20Kamal%20Nath's%20constituency%20from%20where%20the%20Congress%20has%20fielded%20his%20son%20Nakul%20Nath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRajgarh%20has%20been%20breached%2C%20you%20have%20to%20see%20that%20Digvijay%20Singh%20ji%20will%20lose%20with%20record%20votes%2C%20his%20magic%20is%20not%20working%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chouhan%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20he%20said%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister's%20%26quot%3Bcredibility%20is%20in%20serious%20danger%20and%20many%20people%20thought%20that%20if%20he%20is%20leaving%20then%20we%20should%20also%20follow%20him%26quot%3B.%20Many%20of%20them%20did%20finally%20join%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20these%20newcomers%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20said%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20join%20the%20%26quot%3Bmovement%20of%20national%20reconstruction%26quot%3B%20are%20welcome.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20workers%20are%20disappointed%2C%20now%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20left%20in%20the%20Congress%20--%20neither%20leader%2C%20nor%20policy%2C%20nor%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chouhan%20has%20much%20to%20be%20proud%20of%20about%20the%20BJP's%20spectacular%20performance%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20Though%20the%20four-time%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20not%20offered%20the%20top%20job%20again%2C%20he%20now%20has%20his%20task%20cut%20out.%20Mr%20Chouhan%20is%20the%20BJP's%20star%20campaigner%20in%20the%20state%20he%20knows%20like%20the%20back%20of%20his%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2064-year-old%20is%20out%20at%208%20am%20and%20is%20never%20back%20before%202%20in%20the%20night.%20It%20is%20a%20tough%20ask%2C%20but%20Mr%20Chouhan%20has%20the%20experience.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%2C%20he%20addressed%20more%20than%20160%20rallies%20throughout%20the%20state%20in%20roughly%2037%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20is%20a%20meticulously%20planned%20endeavor%2C%20designed%20to%20connect%20with%20voters%20at%20every%20level.%20From%20bustling%20city%20centers%20to%20remote%20villages%2C%20he%20criss-crosses%20his%20constituency%20along%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20state%2C%20addressing%20public%20gatherings%2C%20interacting%20with%20locals%2C%20and%20listening%20to%20their%20concerns.%20His%20oratory%20skills%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20grassroots%20issues%2C%20allow%20him%20to%20strike%20a%20chord%20with%20diverse%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20approach%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan's%20campaign%20resonates%20with%20promises%20of%20progress%2C%20development%2C%20and%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20possible%20outcome%20of%20the%20election%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20said%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20resides%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20people%20do%20not%20just%20consider%20him%20as%20a%20leader%2C%20they%20look%20at%20him%20with%20reverence%20and%20devotion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chouhan%20said%20he%20is%20not%20worried%20about%20his%20own%20seat%2C%20given%20the%20%26quot%3Blove%20and%20blessings%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20people%20he%20has%20received%20over%20the%20last%20three%20terms.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20in%20the%20state%20is%20my%20family%20and%20that%20is%20why%20I%20go%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20leader%20is%20contesting%20from%20Vidisha%20%E2%80%93%20a%20constituency%20he%20represented%20five%20times%20before%20becoming%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20November%202005.%20Currently%2C%20he%20is%20the%20MLA%20from%20the%20Budhni%20assembly%20seat%2C%20which%20is%20under%20the%20Vidisha%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20opponent%20is%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Sharma%20from%20Congress.%20On%20how%20Mr%20Sharma%20had%20challenged%20him%20earlier%20as%20well%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20respect%20the%20dignity%20of%20every%20person%2C%20he%20has%20been%20an%20MP%20twice%20before%2C%20I%20respect%20him%20too%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20political%20career%20spanning%20decades%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20has%20held%20various%20significant%20positions%20within%20the%20BJP%2C%20including%20three%20consecutive%20terms%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712684100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcq7g9998_shivraj-singh-chouhan_625x300_09_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-credibility-in-serious-danger-shivraj-chouhan-on-kamal-nath-5408368%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20record%20loss%20for%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Digvijaya%20Singh%2C%20a%20record%20victory%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Congress's%20last%20citadel%2C%20Chhindwara%20--%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20appeared%20more%20tha