th%20basil%20seeds%2C%20fruits%2C%20herbs%20and%20flowers).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20among%20many%20other%20delicacies%20set%20before%20us%2C%20one%20dish%20reigned%20supreme%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eseviyan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20vermicelli%20pudding%20made%20with%20ghee%2C%20rice%20vermicelli%20noodles%2C%20milk%2C%20spices%2C%20and%20a%20sweetener.%20While%20it%20is%20a%20common%20guest%20at%20the%3Cem%3E%20iftar%3C%2Fem%3E%20feast%2C%20my%20friend%20Thousif%20Raza%20explains%20it%20is%20its%20fancier%20cousin%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esheer%20khurma%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20makes%20an%20appearance%20on%20Eid.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESheer%20khurma%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20made%20with%20extra%20%3Cem%3Ekhoya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(thickened%20milk)%20and%20dry%20fruits%20%E2%80%94%20a%20richer%20version%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Eseviyan%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20nevertheless%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247633%2Fla-kheer-deli-shivang-sood-pune-startup-kheer-indian-traditional-dessert-homemade-recipes-success-story-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreamy%20concoctions%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20fit%20for%20kings.%20Once%20prepared%20for%20royalty%2C%20the%20dish%20reflects%20regional%20sensibilities%2C%20with%20each%20diaspora%20adding%20to%20it%20what%20they%20deem%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20origins%20of%20the%20vermicelli%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20ingredients%20in%20%3Cem%3Eseviyan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20are%20hidden%20by%20the%20passage%20of%20time.%20Translating%20to%20%E2%80%98little%20worms%E2%80%99%2C%20these%20thin%20rice%20noodles%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20diets%20as%20far%20back%20as%20the%201660s.%20And%2C%20each%20cuisine%20has%20embraced%20a%20different%20form%20of%20it%20in%20its%20dishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20706px)%20100vw%2C%20706px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22htt