0decade%20back%20when%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Mukesh%20Maanjoo%2C%20a%20former%20National%20Security%20Guard%20(NSG)%2C%20caught%20on%20to%20this%20fact%2C%20he%20was%20disheartened.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20climatic%20conditions%20of%20both%20Pakistan%20and%20India%20are%20the%20same%2C%20so%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20cultivate%20dates%20ourselves%3F%20We%20should%20lose%20some%20of%20the%20dependency%20on%20other%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelieving%20this%20as%20his%20patriotic%20duty%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335795%2Fisro-project-scientist-divakar-channappa-first-organic-date-farmer-in-karnataka-earns-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivate%20dates%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Pilani.%20Last%20season%2C%20Mukesh%20harvested%20five%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20dates%20which%20earned%20him%20a%20huge%20income%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20his%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20commando%20to%20farmer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20taking%20up%20date%20farming%2C%20Mukesh%20worked%20as%20a%20commando%20at%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%2015%20years.%20He%20specialised%20in%20counter-hijack%20operations%20to%20safeguard%20people.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20took%20voluntary%20retirement%20from%20the%20NSG%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20work%2C%20I%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20visit%2020%20countries.%20On%20my%20way%20from%20the%20airports%20to%20hotels%2C%20I%20would%20spare%20some%20time%20to%20visit%20nearby%20farms%20and%20learn%20about%20their%20technologies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAgriculture%20is%20in%20my%20DNA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20my%20father%20and%20grandfathers%20grow%20crops.%20But%20like%20them%2C%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20grow%20traditional%20crops%20like%20mustard%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20grams.%20I%20wanted%20to%20try%20new%20technologies.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20crops%20that%20required%20less%20water%20to%20grow%20in%20our%20dry%20region%20of%20Rajasthan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mukesh%20says%20Barhi%20and%20Khuneji%20varieties%20give%20high%20yields%20in%20low%20maintenance%20and%20have%20lower%20mortality%20rates%20as%20well.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346770%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMukesh%20says%20Barhi%20and%20Khuneji%20varieties%20give%20high%20yields%20in%20low%20maintenance%20and%20have%20lower%20mortality%20rates%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20as%20a%20commando%2C%20Mukesh%20had%20already%20started%20preparing%20himself%20to%20take%20up%20farming.%20But%20in%202018%2C%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20return%20to%20his%20village%20after%20his%20father%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer.%20%E2%80%9CSix%20months%20later%2C%20my%20father%20lost%20his%20life%20to%20the%20disease.%20His%20last%20advice%20to%20me%20was%20to%20take%20up%20date%20farming%20for%20a%20profitable%20farming%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20he%20undertook%20a%203-day%20training%20programme%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20Excellence%20for%20Date%20Palm%20at%20Sagra-Bhojka%20in%20the%20Jaisalmer%20district.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20state%20government%20was%20promoting%20date%20cultivation%20in%20Rajasthan%20by%20distributing%20subsidised%20date%20palm%20saplings%20to%20farmers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20procured%20250%20date%20palm%20seeds%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342788%2Fyellow-dates-farming-in-india-engineer-quits-job-to-become-an-agripreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyellow-coloured%20Barhi%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20red-coloured%20Khuneji%20varieties%20and%20planted%20them%20on%20his%20farmland.%20It%20took%20four%20years%20before%20he%20saw%20the%20first%20fruit%20on%20the%20date%20palm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20grow%20money%20on%20trees%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20points%20out%20that%20growing%20dates%20have%20been%20extremely%20fruitful%20as%20both%20Barhi%20and%20Khuneji%20varieties%20give%20high%20yields%20in%20low%20maintenance%20and%20have%20lower%20mortality%20rates%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20plant%20say%20100%20trees%2C%20then%20only%201-2%20will%20die.%20The%20remaining%20trees%20will%20survive%20and%20continue%20to%20yield%20for%2080%20years.%20Besides%2C%20once%20the%20seeds%20are%20sown%2C%20we%20are%20only%20required%20to%20provide%20organic%20manures%20like%20cow%20and%20goat%20dung.%20Every%20year%2C%20I%20just%20add%20150%20kg%20of%20manure%20to%20one%20tree%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%2