2Fkerala-aluva-seed-farm-first-in-india-to-become-carbon-neutral%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20methods%20of%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20father%20introduced%20chemicals%20and%20pesticides%2C%20which%20Saravanan%20continued%20till%202006%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20introduced%20the%20micro-irrigation%20scheme%20in%202005-06%2C%20under%20which%20subsidies%20were%20provided%20for%20drip%20and%20sprinkler%20irrigation.%20Saravanan%2C%20an%20early%20adopter%20of%20many%20such%20new%3Cbr%3Eschemes%2C%20decided%20to%20give%20drip%20irrigation%20a%20try.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20face%20water%20scarcity%2C%20which%20made%20irrigation%20very%20difficult.%20Drip%20irrigation%20saves%20water%20and%20irrigates%20thrice%20the%20amount%20of%20land%20using%20the%20same%20water%20used%20by%20traditional%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saravanan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202007%2C%20the%20farmer%20has%20moved%20to%20drip%20irrigation%20on%20his%206%20acre%20and%2036%20cents%20(1%20acre%20is%20100%20cents)%20land%20on%20which%20he%20cultivates%20turmeric%2C%20groundnuts%2C%20and%20vegetables.%20He%20also%20practises%20integrated%20farming%2C%20a%20sustainable%20agricultural%20system%20where%20crops%2C%20livestock%2C%20aquaculture%2C%20poultry%20are%20managed%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20these%20crops%2C%20he%20also%20manages%20livestock%2C%20including%20cows%2C%20goats%2C%20ducks%20and%20birds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20he%20started%20drip%20irrigation%2C%20he%20got%20his%20soil%20tested.%20The%20test%20indicated%20that%20the%20soil%20was%20not%20healthy%2C%20and%20had%20rising%20pH%20levels%20and%20was%20getting%20spoilt.%20This%20was%20the%20same%20time%20when%20his%20turmeric%20crop%20was%20affected%20by%20diseases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%2