80%99t%20the%20buzzword%20that%20it%20is%20today%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263077%2Fbest-food-kolkata-famous-pice-hotels-history-british-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20%3Cem%3Epice%3C%2Fem%3E%20hotels%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20acing%20the%20game.%20The%20story%20goes%20that%20to%20keep%20operating%20costs%20low%20while%20continuing%20to%20maintain%20a%20profitable%20business%2C%20these%20hotels%20toyed%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20seasonal%20eating%20while%20prioritising%20fresh%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20waste%20was%20not%20tolerated%20and%20every%20part%20of%20the%20produce%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20bones%20to%20the%20peel%20%E2%80%94%20was%20used.%20Sometimes%20food%20would%20be%20served%20in%20banana%20leaves%20to%20eliminate%20plate%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Epice%3C%2Fem%3E%20hotels%20were%20united%20in%20the%20way%20they%20displayed%20their%20menus%20depending%20on%20the%20produce%20that%20was%20available%20in%20the%20market%20that%20day.%20The%20items%20for%20the%20day%20would%20then%20make%20it%20to%20a%20board%20at%20the%20entrance%20that%20the%20guests%20could%20look%20at.%20It%20was%20an%20amusing%20sight%20to%20watch%20the%20servers%20rattle%20off%20the%20whole%20list%20from%20memory%2C%20despite%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295149%2Ficonic-restaurants-of-kolkata-mancherjis-serves-best-parsi-food-started-in-home-kitchen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20menu%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20ever-changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCw9WBMTPl3D%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCw9