.com%2F311908%2Fstory-and-making-of-goyna-gohona-bori-bengali-side-dish-rabindranath-tagore-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaste%20of%20originals%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20preserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustomers%20flocking%20to%20the%20hotel%20rave%20about%20the%20%3Cem%3Ealu%20bhaja%20%3C%2Fem%3E(crispy%20fried%20potato%20slices)%2C%20%3Cem%3Emacher%20dim%20er%20bora%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fritters%20prepared%20with%20fish%20eggs)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ealu%20kumro%20chokha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20Bengali-style%20sweet%20pumpkin%20curry)%2C%20%3Cem%3Echingri%20macher%20malaikari%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20Bengali%20curry%20made%20from%20Tiger%20prawns)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhashir%20mangsho%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Bengali%20mutton%20curry)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Echitol%20macher%20muitha%20bora%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Bengali%20fish%20curry)%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20though%20popularly%20hailed%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Swadhin%20Bharat%20Hindu%20Hotel%E2%80%99%2C%20this%20was%20not%20the%20eatery%E2%80%99s%20original%20name.%20It%20was%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Hotel%E2%80%99%20in%201912%20when%20it%20was%20established%20by%20a%20gentleman%20named%20Mangobindo%20Panda.%20The%20name%20was%20changed%20following%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F187763%2Findia-freedom-struggle-independence-unsung-heroes-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndependence%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20Panda%20marked%20the%20occasion%20by%20renaming%20the%20hotel%20%E2%80%98Swadhin%20Bharat%20Hindu%20Hotel%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ode%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20600px)%20100vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-06-at-10.05.00-PM-2-1710505323.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose's%20favourite%20del