0begins%20in%20the%20City%20of%20Joy%2C%20the%20first%20trickle%20of%20guests%20begins%20to%20enter%20the%20Swadhin%20Bharat%20Hindu%20Hotel%2C%20which%20is%20carrying%20the%20baton%20of%20its%20legacy%20forward%2C%20not%20just%20in%20its%20food%20but%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294513%2Frare-pictures-of-india-history-freedom-struggle-independence-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20tales%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20every%20guest%20is%20treated%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711973034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344968%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Swadhin%20Bharat%20Hindu%20Hotel%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20started%20by%20Mangobindo%20Panda%2C%20is%20a%20century-old%20pice%20hotel%20where%20Indian%20freedom%20fighters%20like%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%20would%20enjoy%20Bengali%20delicacies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344968%2Fswadhin-bharat-hindu-pice-hotel-kolkata-bengali-cuisine-netaji-subhas-chandra-bose-history%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20a%20Turnover%20of%20Rs%203%20Crore%2C%20Couple%20Has%20Made%20Over%20a%20Million%20Eco-Friendly%20Bags%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20their%20corporate%20jobs%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Chennai%2C%20Gowri%20Gopinath%20and%20Krishnan%20Subramanian%2C%20both%20longed%20to%20return%20to%20their%20hometown%2C%20Madurai%2C%20and%20embrace%20a%20minimalist%20lifestyle.%20The%20couple%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20the%20rising%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295063%2Fsustainable-startup-recharkha-by-amita-deshpande-upcycles-plastic-wrappers-into-bags%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20pollution%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20looked%20around%2C%20we%20felt%20that%20there%20is%20this%20huge%20consumption%20culture%20that%20is%20highly%20dependent%20on%20plastics%2C%20especially%20single-use.%20We%20were%20a%20part%20of%20it%20too.%20We%20reflected%20on%20this%20thought%20and%20realised%20the%20need%20for%20switching%20from%20plastics%20to%20something%20eco-friendly%20and%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishnan%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20decided%20to%20start%20YellowBag%20%E2%80%94%20a%20cloth%20bag%20venture%20in%202014.%20They%20started%20small%20by%20educating%20their%20friends%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250207%2Faparna-krishnan-paalaguttapalle-bags-eco-friendly-hand-stitched-bags-andhra-pradesh-women-empowerment-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20families%20to%20use%20cloth%20bags.%3C%2Fa%3E%20They%20collaborated%20with%20local%20tailors%20to%20make%20the%20bags%20and%20meet%20the%20steadily%20growing%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20quit%20their%20respective%20jobs%20and%20throw%20themselves%20into%20growing%20their%20venture.%20The%20name%20comes%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F276764%2Fmadurai-couple-quits-jobs-eco-friendly-cloth-manjapai-yellow-bag-plastic-alternative%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20Manjappai%3C%2Fa%3E%20(which%20means%20a%20yellow-coloured%20cloth%20bag)%2C%20which%20has%20always%20been%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Tamil%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20revive%20this%20tradition%2C%20the%20company%20offers%20a%20range%20of%20eco-friendly%20and%20sustainable%20bags%20made%20of%20cotton%20and%20jute%20that%20serve%20different%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20offer%20products%20li